<h2>Reset your password</h2>

<p>Hello <%= @user.first_name || @user.email %>,</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your <%= @application_name %> account.</p>

<div class="highlight-box">
  <p><strong>Password Reset Request</strong></p>
  <p>Click the button below to choose a new password for your account.</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= @reset_password_url %>" class="btn">Reset My Password</a>
</p>

<p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px;">
  <%= @reset_password_url %>
</p>

<p><strong>Important security notes:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>This password reset link will expire in 2 hours</li>
  <li>For your security, you'll need to confirm your current password when setting a new one</li>
  <li>If you didn't request this reset, you can safely ignore this email</li>
</ul>

<p>If you're having trouble or didn't request this password reset, please contact our support team immediately.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The <%= @application_name %> Team</p>